title: SUN RA SPEAKS - HIS POETRY

http_headers.User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/72.0.3623.2 Safari/537.36

description:
Sunny, right along with the music, was always writing his poetry. Not once do I recall Sunny ever sitting dormant. Time was very precious and each moment was filled with creating and developing an idea in his vast creative mind.

To hear Sunny speak is just a small window into the world of his thoughts. The sincerity in his voice and the conviction behind his mission, in writing only scrapes a minuscule part of  the whirling spectrum of his words of wisdom.
